job_details.Functieomschrijving:
As a senior software engineer, you will be working in the Data Science Innovation department. You will be part of a team with data scientists that focus on innovation with data science. The team aims to help PostNL make great strides in data science and generative AI. You will take the lead in developing innovative solutions, collaborating with experts, and advancing technology in this domain. We are looking for someone with effective communication skills, who likes to work together and has a passion for learning and sharing knowledge. Moreover, you will be part of the PostNL engineering community in which we share "best practices" and innovations in our company.
   What you will be doing
     * Lead the ideation, design, and deployment of innovative solutions in data science and generative AI;
     * Develop creative and forward-thinking functionalities for Data Science platforms;
     * Optimize code efficiency and investigate novel, high-speed solutions;
     * Drive innovation in data science technologies, fostering a culture of continuous improvement;
     * Explore new AWS services and optimize product performance through experimentation and testing;
     * Mentor and teach colleagues, actively sharing your software engineering knowledge;
     * Provide expertise in building and maintaining a code library, emphasizing best practices and innovation;
     * Automate security checks and build robust CI/CD pipelines, championing efficiency and reliability;
     * Collaborate on the development of AWS SDK solutions, pushing the boundaries of what is possible.

   Our ambition
   PostNL aims to be the favorite logistics company.The ambition of the team is to help PostNL make great strides by innovating in the domain of data science and AI and help them be the favorite logistics company.

